room_title: Escape room "The Legend of Lyndale House" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: The Legend of Lyndale House isn't a puzzle room - this is a puzzle house. A team of 5-16 must work together to unravel this chilling supernatural tale. This isn't a "Haunted House", so don't expect blood and gore or people in cheap halloween masks to pop out at you. That being said, this experience certainly isn't without creepy elements, tension, and dread. Beware!
